            text = "ikh bin arayn tsu im in shtub. er hot zikh zeyer interesirt, er hot zikh zeyer shtark interesirt vegn di yidn velkhe zenen geven in lager. ikh hob im dertseylt vegn zikh, vegn mayne eltern," 
